Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,默默地为你着想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是悄悄藏在你看不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以平时毫无察觉地生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一旦回过神来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你着想的那个人的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会朦胧地浮现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果激烈地浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们就称之为…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦～？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.28,0:00:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 我今天做了烤奶油马铃薯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想让爸爸妈妈吃到好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坑坑洼洼的 样子糟糕得不好意思拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.96,0:00:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 一点也不会糟糕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为里面充满了小爱的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为蓝华今天去参加公司员工的旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只有我跟爱丽丝两个人一起练习
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使的歌声…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的声音好好听 好好听哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为领航员最重要的是划船的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 难道你心情不好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让比你年长的我来听你倾诉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事都不要客气 告诉姐姐吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…我的左手太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近发觉我的左手非常笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟右手比 既无法拿好筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没办法写出端正的字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那个…有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我正在惩罚左手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太依赖右手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都把所有事情交给右手做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还把这当作理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没有想办法解决过这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近养了一只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:03:00.03,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 想要守护的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是领航员协会中最顶尖的橙色行星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是宿舍严禁养宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没关系吗？爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左手特训？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它嘛嘛地叫 就取名为小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天前它被丢弃在路边时 被我捡回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你一个很寂寞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才找我商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来想找蓝华前辈商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不巧她去公司员工的旅行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才找了灯里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带回我们公司里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会给亚利亚社长圆不隆咚的肚子造成大危机的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛 别叫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不是奇怪的人…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是跟我同寝室的雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是跟你说进房间前要敲门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓我一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才被你吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰你了 我是亚利亚公司的水无灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一位是我们公司的亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？爱丽丝 雅典娜前辈是不是长得跟刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一位唱着美妙歌声的人有一点像？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 就是她本人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在三大精灵之中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就属雅典娜前辈的Canzone最为有名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}Canzone：意大利语「歌」的意思 这里特指船歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人就是传说中的雅典娜前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈要住下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前请先换上本公司的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那样超级显眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 小嘛会不会被雅典娜前辈发现呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前为止都还能应付过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为雅典娜前辈超级喜欢发呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇…好像豪华餐厅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一日三餐大都是在这里解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 这杯水是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没发觉是雅典娜前辈帮她拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈又把全部的奶精放下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好甜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看雅典娜前辈那样 她可是个很笨拙的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常在走廊上跌倒 还经常把饮料打翻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是连最重要的事情都会忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打电话的时候还会自己不小心把电话挂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说她有多笨拙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概跟我的左手差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:08:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 不可以这样说自己的前辈啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们两个都完全不在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚会跟亚利亚社长在您宿舍暂住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是爱找麻烦 这时候就要用左手…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 请您先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛 吃饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗？小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小嘛的事告诉雅典娜前辈也没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 因为就算是前辈也改不了规定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你打算把它就这么藏着养吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要这么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久前 橙色行星的社长去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到小嘛就会想起它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位社长跟小嘛很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 一点也不像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 哎呀… 前辈洗得舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说应该已经暴露了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢？爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的猜拳游戏…当然输的都是左手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在黑漆漆的地方会不会寂寞呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛在哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能…败露了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈的歌唱得真是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 左手可能没你想的那么笨拙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈今天公司休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在衣橱里面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去上学了 前辈请慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这能持续到什么时候呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}这就是移居的一大原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}好 正如上次课堂上所说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}大规模的AQUA移居计划其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}已经是五十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}在那之前积累了无数次的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为昨天那件事 可能已经有人发现小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左手可能没你想的那么笨拙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左手总是在背后默默地支持着…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 我是今天起跟您同室的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝·卡罗尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛…小嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛它…小嘛它…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:16:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底去哪了呢？小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是被雅典娜前辈发现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后告诉公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…不能把事情往坏的地方想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到猫了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到爱丽丝的房间传来猫的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以打开了衣橱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后它就逃跑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…不是雅典娜前辈丢掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈早就察觉到小嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是为了掩饰小嘛的哭声才特意唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…比左手还要没用…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连小嘛都保护不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:18:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你回来 小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小嘛也显得很安心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对小嘛而言 爱丽丝也是重要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 找到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道您刚才唱歌是为了找小嘛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:20:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也是为了掩饰小嘛的哭声吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都没察觉到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚住进宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为害怕 睡不着的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时你也是这样唱着歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是…还有 在我失眠的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也总是像这样 是为我而唱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为歌声…是要传达给别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去跟公司商量过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你注意到了吗？虽然太小不易察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这孩子确实拥有蓝色的眼睛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子将成为橙色行星的新社长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色眼睛的守护神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左手…是超级伟大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在开始要练习向左手道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 我把烤奶油马铃薯忘在厨房里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知什么时候被爸爸吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下了一张字条…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写着「味道还可以 我期待你下次的作品」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便吃人家的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟说「还可以」 这算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很过分对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也因此从低落中走了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心变得很温暖 真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 可能我们大家不知何时起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也在被别人默默支持着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人无法察觉地 默默地…悄悄地…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.64,0:23:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能坐上晃前辈的凤尾舟？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能这么高兴也只有现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:23:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份 美好的工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起度过美好的时光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:01:01.97,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}頬をなでる 優しい風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:11.15,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}波音に 揺られて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:20.76,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}体の中 ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:31.50,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}目を閉じて 見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:39.78,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}風の行く道が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:49.89,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}さあ 漕ぎ出そう 光る波へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:59.03,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}笑顏が すぐ こぼれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:09.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ねえ 伝えよう このときめき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:19.78,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}風にのって あなたのもとへ 行くわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:23.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}ウンディーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:01:01.97,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}轻拂面颊的 温柔的风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:11.15,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}在海浪的歌声中摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:20.76,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 融入身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:31.50,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}闭上双眼 看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:39.78,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}是风的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:49.89,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}来 让我们出发 向着闪亮的波涛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:59.03,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}脸上的笑容 从未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:09.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}快 传达到彼方 把这份感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:19.78,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}托付给清风 带到你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:23.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}水之精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:29.36,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}水辺に映る いつもの景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:36.93,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}穏やかに 流れる時間と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:40.64,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}移りゆく 季節の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:48.65,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}見つけたの 変わらぬ想いを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:52.95,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}聴いて 幸せの歌は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:59.56,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}そう いつでも 心の中あふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:08.13,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:11.40,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:19.31,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:25.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:33.52,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:40.16,OPEDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:29.36,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不变的景色 倒映在水边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:36.93,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}在缓缓流逝的时光和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:40.64,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}不断变化的季节中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:48.65,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}寻觅到 那不变的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:52.95,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}听 那幸福的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:59.56,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}像这样 一直 满溢于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:08.13,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}所有的梦想 都将实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:11.40,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我们 总会越过彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:19.31,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}雨后的彩虹 清澄的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:25.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}相信那青鸟 总会展翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:33.52,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}收集起胸中的爱意 定会见到彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:40.16,OPEDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}心中常怀爱意 定能越过彩虹
